# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CONTACT FORM CONFIGURATION
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# OPTION A — Formspree (recommended, no backend needed)
# 1. Sign up free at https://formspree.io using hakiza@vestafi.africa
# 2. Create a new form, copy its endpoint (looks like https://formspree.io/f/abcwxyz)
# 3. Set the variable below and redeploy.
#
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=

# OPTION B — SMTP fallback (only used when the Formspree var above is blank)
# Used by app/api/contact/route.js via nodemailer.
#
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.your-provider.com
# SMTP_PORT=587
# SMTP_USER=you@example.com
# SMTP_PASS=your-app-password
# CONTACT_TO=hakiza@vestafi.africa
# CONTACT_FROM=you@example.com
